<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>CRS Score for Education 2026 — How Education Affects Your Express Entry Points</h1>
    <p>Education is worth up to 150 CRS points (PhD, no spouse). A two-or-more degree/diploma at master's level earns 135 points, a 3-year bachelor's earns 120 points, and a high school diploma earns just 28 points. Know your exact score and what Canadian education adds.</p>
    <div class="pill-row">
      <span class="pill">Updated April 2026</span>
      <span class="pill">Max 150 Education Points</span>
      <span class="pill">With & Without Spouse</span>
      <span class="pill">AEO Optimised</span>
